14:51.100 --> 14:53.900
They were out no money,
they bought nothing,

14:53.967 --> 14:55.967
they really didn't spend
a lot of time with you

14:56.100 --> 14:57.834
other than they would
with any customer,

14:58.200 --> 15:00.367
just as the first time
you spoke to him.

